collectionMetadata.name: Singapore Police Force Digital Speed Enforcement Cameras
collectionMetadata.description: Digital Speed Enforcement Camera System (DSECS) consists of SPF wholly owned traffic enforcement cameras deployed along major roads to deter and detect vehicles from committing the traffic offence of speeding. Implementation is in progress. Note that the speed enforcement cameras under LTA''s purview are excluded in this list.
